OL,3,CMan's body found in plane's landing
OL,4,Cgear at Gatwick Airport
OL,6,FA man's body has been recovered from
OL,7,Fthe landing gear of a plane at Gatwick
OL,8,FAirport.
OL,10,FThe discovery was made on Tuesday
OL,11,Fmorning, following the arrival of an
OL,12,FAir Arabia flight.
OL,14,FSussex Police said the flight had
OL,15,Fdeparted from Tangier, in Morocco.
OL,17,FThe force has opened an investigation
OL,18,Fand will prepare a report for the
OL,19,Fcoroner.
