OL,3,CMan's body found in plane's landing
OL,4,Cgear at Gatwick Airport
OL,6,FThe identity of the man has not been
OL,7,Freleased.
OL,9,FA London Gatwick spokesperson said:
OL,10,F"London Gatwick's emergency services
OL,11,Fattended an Air Arabia aircraft just
OL,12,Fafter 11.30am yesterday (June 16 2026)
OL,13,Fwhen an incident was identified upon
OL,14,Farrival.
OL,16,F"As Sussex Police confirmed, a body
OL,17,Fwas found and our teams subsequently
OL,18,Fsupported Sussex Police and the
OL,19,Fcoroner.
